name: ruralidyll 009
description:
I normally draw from my imaginings, channelling some idealised abstracted cartoon. 

This is a rare (for me) en plein air drawing, sat on the beach opposite Es Vedrà. 

I have included the sketch and final directly as drawn in my notebook; after all of my third eye dreaming and magik imaginings, I love this raw and scruffy picture-in-picture comicstrip effect.
